</style>

<div class="lp-reloc scheme-default">
  {%- render 'bbi-nav', logo: section.settings.logo, active: 'services' -%}

  {%- render 'bbi-crumbs', c2_label: 'Relocation Management' -%}


  {%- comment -%} Hero {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-hero">
    <div class="lp-hero__inner">
      <div class="lp-hero__text">
        <div class="lp-hero__eyebrow">
          <span class="bbi-mono lp-hero__eyebrow-label">Services &middot; Relocation Management</span>
        </div>
        <h1>One project team. Vacate, decommission, install &mdash; without taking your operations offline.</h1>
        <p class="lp-hero__standfirst">Brant Business Interiors runs office relocations end-to-end &mdash; not just the furniture moving piece. Inventory audit, decommission, responsible disposal, phased install in your new space, post-move punch-list. Family-owned since 1964 &mdash; the project coordinator who scopes your move is the one who runs it. Multi-site and multi-floor moves a specialty.</p>
        <div class="lp-hero__cta-row">
          <a href="/pages/quote" class="bbi-btn bbi-btn--primary bbi-btn--lg">Request a Quote <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          <a href="tel:18008359565" class="bbi-btn bbi-btn--secondary bbi-btn--lg">1-800-835-9565</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-hero__media">
        {%- if section.settings.hero_image != blank -%}
          {{ section.settings.hero_image | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'eager', alt: 'Office relocation and furniture installation' }}
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="lp-hero__ph"><span class="bbi-mono">Relocation hero image</span></div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Intro {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-intro">
    <div class="lp-intro__inner">
      <div class="lp-intro__eyebrow">
        <span class="bbi-mono">Full-scope relocation</span>
      </div>
      <h2>Move your office without moving your team off-track.</h2>
      <div class="lp-intro__body">
        <p>Brant Business Interiors is the family-run Ontario office furniture dealer most buyers know us by. The legal entity behind our OECM agreement is <b>Brant Basics</b> &mdash; same team, same address at 296 George St N, Peterborough. Family-owned since 1964; we run relocations as a single project, not a hand-off between vendors.</p>
        <p>Office relocations fail when logistics aren&rsquo;t coordinated. We manage the complete scope &mdash; furniture decommission, inventory audit, responsible disposal or resale, phased install in the new space, and post-move punch-list. Your facilities team isn&rsquo;t juggling three contractors. One project coordinator, one Ontario account team, from PO to staff move-in day.</p>
        <p>Whether you&rsquo;re moving a 10-person office, a multi-floor institutional site, or coordinating phased moves across multiple buildings, the project plan is built around your occupancy dates and operational access windows. OECM Agreement 2025-470 covers relocation services for eligible Ontario broader-public-sector buyers &mdash; no separate tender required.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Browse-categories crosslinks (Session A standardization) {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-crosslinks" aria-label="Browse furniture categories for your new space">
    <div class="lp-crosslinks__inner">
      <div class="lp-crosslinks__head">
        <p class="lp-crosslinks__eyebrow bbi-mono">Browse categories</p>
        <h2>Refreshing or replacing? Browse the catalog for your new space.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-crosslinks__grid">
        <a href="/collections/seating" class="lp-crosslinks__tile">
