  {%- comment -%} Process Steps {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-process">
    <div class="lp-process__inner">
      <div class="lp-process__head">
        <div class="lp-process__eyebrow">
          <span class="bbi-mono">How it works</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Four phases from vacating to move-in day</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-process__grid">
        <div class="lp-process-card">
          <p class="lp-process-card__step">Phase 01</p>
          <h3 class="lp-process-card__title">Inventory &amp; planning</h3>
          <p class="lp-process-card__body">We audit your existing furniture, identify what moves, what disposes, and what replaces. A phased project plan is built around your occupancy dates and facility access windows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-process-card">
          <p class="lp-process-card__step">Phase 02</p>
          <h3 class="lp-process-card__title">Decommission &amp; disposal</h3>
          <p class="lp-process-card__body">Our team removes, packs, and responsibly disposes of or donates outgoing furniture. We handle coordination with your building management for dock access and disposal logistics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-process-card">
          <p class="lp-process-card__step">Phase 03</p>
          <h3 class="lp-process-card__title">New-space installation</h3>
          <p class="lp-process-card__body">All new and relocated furniture is installed to your approved floor plan. Workstations assembled, seating adjusted, and cable management completed before your staff arrives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-process-card">
          <p class="lp-process-card__step">Phase 04</p>
          <h3 class="lp-process-card__title">Post-move punch-list</h3>
          <p class="lp-process-card__body">We return to address any adjustments, missing items, or warranty concerns within the first two weeks of occupancy. The job isn't done until your team is settled.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} OECM Bar {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="lp-oecm-bar">
    <div class="lp-oecm-bar__inner">
      <span class="lp-oecm-bar__badge">OECM Supplier</span>
      <p class="lp-oecm-bar__text"><strong>OECM Agreement 2025-470</strong> — Ontario schools, hospitals, and government offices can engage relocation services through OECM without an open tender process. <a href="/pages/oecm" style="color:var(--saleBadgeBackground);font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">Learn about OECM purchasing →</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {%- comment -%} Top Products (Session A standardization) {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign tp1 = section.settings.top_product_1 -%}
  {%- assign tp2 = section.settings.top_product_2 -%}
  {%- assign tp3 = section.settings.top_product_3 -%}
  {%- assign tp4 = section.settings.top_product_4 -%}
  {%- if tp1 == blank -%}{%- assign tp1 = collections['height-adjustable-tables-desks'].products.first -%}{%- endif -%}
  {%- if tp1 == blank -%}{%- assign tp1 = collections.desks.products.first -%}{%- endif -%}
  {%- if tp2 == blank -%}{%- assign tp2 = collections.seating.products.first -%}{%- endif -%}
  {%- if tp3 == blank -%}{%- assign tp3 = collections.storage.products.first -%}{%- endif -%}
  {%- if tp4 == blank -%}{%- assign tp4 = collections.boardroom.products.first -%}{%- endif -%}
  {%- if tp4 == blank -%}{%- assign tp4 = collections.tables.products.first -%}{%- endif -%}
  <section class="lp-products" aria-label="Top relocation refresh picks">
    <div class="lp-products__inner">
      <div class="lp-products__head">
        <p class="lp-products__eyebrow">Top refresh picks</p>
        <h2>{{ section.settings.top_products_heading | default: 'Refreshing during the move? These are the most-quoted swaps.' }}</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-products__grid">
        {%- if tp1 != blank and tp1 != nil -%}<article class="lp-product-card"><a class="lp-product-card__media" href="{{ tp1.url }}">{%- if tp1.featured_image -%}{{ tp1.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 | image_tag: alt: tp1.title, loading: 'lazy', width: 600 }}{%- endif -%}</a><div class="lp-product-card__body"><p class="lp-product-card__vendor">{{ tp1.vendor }}</p><h3 class="lp-product-card__title"><a href="{{ tp1.url }}">{{ tp1.title }}</a></h3><p class="lp-product-card__price">From {{ tp1.price_min | money }}</p><a class="lp-product-card__cta" href="{{ tp1.url }}">View product</a></div></article>{%- endif -%}
        {%- if tp2 != blank and tp2 != nil -%}<article class="lp-product-card"><a class="lp-product-card__media" href="{{ tp2.url }}">{%- if tp2.featured_image -%}{{ tp2.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 | image_tag: alt: tp2.title, loading: 'lazy', width: 600 }}{%- endif -%}</a><div class="lp-product-card__body"><p class="lp-product-card__vendor">{{ tp2.vendor }}</p><h3 class="lp-product-card__title"><a href="{{ tp2.url }}">{{ tp2.title }}</a></h3><p class="lp-product-card__price">From {{ tp2.price_min | money }}</p><a class="lp-product-card__cta" href="{{ tp2.url }}">View product</a></div></article>{%- endif -%}
        {%- if tp3 != blank and tp3 != nil -%}<article class="lp-product-card"><a class="lp-product-card__media" href="{{ tp3.url }}">{%- if tp3.featured_image -%}{{ tp3.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 | image_tag: alt: tp3.title, loading: 'lazy', width: 600 }}{%- endif -%}</a><div class="lp-product-card__body"><p class="lp-product-card__vendor">{{ tp3.vendor }}</p><h3 class="lp-product-card__title"><a href="{{ tp3.url }}">{{ tp3.title }}</a></h3><p class="lp-product-card__price">From {{ tp3.price_min | money }}</p><a class="lp-product-card__cta" href="{{ tp3.url }}">View product</a></div></article>{%- endif -%}
        {%- if tp4 != blank and tp4 != nil -%}<article class="lp-product-card"><a class="lp-product-card__media" href="{{ tp4.url }}">{%- if tp4.featured_image -%}{{ tp4.featured_image | image_url: width: 600 | image_tag: alt: tp4.title, loading: 'lazy', width: 600 }}{%- endif -%}</a><div class="lp-product-card__body"><p class="lp-product-card__vendor">{{ tp4.vendor }}</p><h3 class="lp-product-card__title"><a href="{{ tp4.url }}">{{ tp4.title }}</a></h3><p class="lp-product-card__price">From {{ tp4.price_min | money }}</p><a class="lp-product-card__cta" href="{{ tp4.url }}">View product</a></div></article>{%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Entity note (Session A / AI-8 standardization) {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-entity-note" aria-label="Legal entity and registration">
    <div class="lp-entity-note__inner">
      <p><b>Brant Business Interiors</b> is the operating brand of <b>Brant Basics</b>, our OECM-registered legal entity holding Supplier Partner Agreement 2025-470. Family-owned since 1964, headquartered at 296 George St N, Peterborough, ON K9J 3H2. Part of the Office Central group.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} FAQ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-faq">
    <div class="lp-faq__inner">
      <div class="lp-faq__head">
        <div class="lp-faq__eyebrow">
          <span class="bbi-mono">Common questions</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Relocation management — FAQ</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="lp-faq__list">
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Do you handle both the old space and the new space?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Yes. Full-scope relocation covers decommissioning the existing space and full installation in the new one. We coordinate both sides of the move under one project manager so nothing falls through the cracks between contractors.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Can you move furniture we didn't purchase from you?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Yes. Our relocation services aren't limited to furniture we originally supplied. We inventory, move, and reinstall your existing pieces alongside any new furniture included in your project. Send us a rough inventory and we&rsquo;ll quote both the move scope and any replacement spec in one quote.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            What happens to furniture we're replacing?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>We can arrange responsible disposal, donation to registered non-profits, or resale depending on the condition of items. For institutional clients with surplus asset policies, we'll work within your disposal requirements. Ask about this during your quote call.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            How far in advance should we engage you for a relocation?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>For a typical office relocation, we recommend engaging us 8&ndash;12 weeks before your occupancy date. Larger institutional moves (full-floor or multi-site) benefit from 12&ndash;20 weeks of lead time. Contact us early &mdash; we can fit a scoping call into 1 business day.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Can you sequence moves across multiple sites or floors?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Yes. Multi-site and multi-floor moves are common for school boards (summer relocations across multiple buildings), hospital wing reconfigurations, and municipal office consolidations. Our project coordinator builds a phased schedule that respects occupancy dates, dock-access windows, and operational continuity at each site. One PM for the whole project &mdash; not a hand-off between site teams.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="lp-faq__item">
          <button class="lp-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
            Can the move happen after-hours or on weekends?
            <span class="lp-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="lp-faq__a">
            <p>Yes. For occupied clinics, operating hospital units, live municipal offices, and school summer windows, after-hours and weekend moves are standard. We schedule around your operations and your facility access requirements. Mention your operational constraints at quote time and we&rsquo;ll build the schedule accordingly &mdash; no premium charged for off-hours work on most projects (we&rsquo;ll flag if your scope adds cost).</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} CTA Closer {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-closer scheme-inverse" style="background:var(--background);padding:var(--space-12) 0;">
    <div class="lp-closer__inner">
      <h2>Planning a move? Let&rsquo;s scope it.</h2>
      <p class="lp-closer__sub">Request a quote and our project team will reach out within 1 business day to scope your relocation. OECM-eligible. Family-owned since 1964 &mdash; one project coordinator from PO to staff move-in day.</p>
      <div class="lp-closer__cta-row">
        <a href="/pages/quote" class="bbi-btn bbi-btn--primary bbi-btn--lg">Request a Quote <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
        <a href="tel:18008359565" class="bbi-btn bbi-btn--secondary bbi-btn--lg">Call 1-800-835-9565</a>
      </div>
      <p class="lp-closer__trust">OECM Agreement 2025-470 &middot; Full-scope relocation &middot; Multi-site &middot; After-hours / weekend windows available</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  {%- render 'bbi-footer', logo: section.settings.logo -%}

</div>

<script>
(function(){
  document.querySelectorAll('.lp-reloc .lp-faq__q').forEach(function(btn){
    btn.addEventListener('click',function(){
      var item=this.closest('.lp-faq__item');
      var open=item.classList.contains('is-open');
      document.querySelectorAll('.lp-reloc .lp-faq__item.is-open').forEach(function(i){i.classList.remove('is-open');i.querySelector('.lp-faq__q').setAttribute('aria-expanded','false');});
      if(!open){item.classList.add('is-open');this.setAttribute('aria-expanded','true');}
    });
  });
})();
</script>

